{"tid":2361528,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港府瞞六年 保安局首披露  大帽山雷達站 駐軍作「防務」","createTime":"2021-01-10T17:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T17:39:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64f681e4e60492760626ce70bd32e5169ed755ff","tid":2361528,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:34:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/FXW5ATBWGNCIRE6K5MTCWFYETA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2FFXW5ATBWGNCIRE6K5MTCWFYETA%2F&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7V95pAf34VZm09NJx5vbAww%3D&h=a8db9def\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210110%2FFXW5ATBWGNCIRE6K5MTCWFYETA%2F&h=686d31d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210110/FXW5ATBWGNCIRE6K5MTCWFYETA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港府瞞六年 保安局首披露 <br />\n大帽山雷達站 駐軍作「防務」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】大帽山雷達站驚現「听党话 跟党走」等簡體字後，保安局昨回覆該處不屬軍事用地，但用途包括用作防務；換言之證實雷達站供解放軍使用，但名義上不是「軍事用地」。港府「隱瞞」六年後，不認不認還須認，有民主派直斥當局砌詞狡辯。軍事專家亦質疑，有更多類似土地撥予解放軍，但市民無從得知。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：無緣睹霜凍 行山客照狂歡<br />\n<br />\n涉事大帽山山頂雷達站，外圍圍繞鐵絲網，入口豎立「此區禁止任何未得許可者進入」告示牌。建築物外牆出現「听党话 跟党走」、「法纪严 风气正」等紅色簡體字，亦有穿迷彩軍服人員駐守，附近山坡畫有五星紅旗。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jubEDg8rlWd0-rBokeLUNAzXUUQ=/2541x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MEPDHVQDLFCPBMKZL5SOKUU6CY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjubEDg8rlWd0-rBokeLUNAzXUUQ%3D%2F2541x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMEPDHVQDLFCPBMKZL5SOKUU6CY.jpg&h=5f2e19b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大帽山雷達站近日驚現「听党话 跟党走」紅色標語，有市民專程前往打卡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷斥保安局狡辯<br />\n<br />\n保安局又指「《基本法》第14條訂明，中央人民政府負責管理香港防務。根據《中華人民共和國香港特別行政區駐軍法》第10條，香港政府應當支持香港駐軍履行防務職責。」換言之證實雷達站是給駐港解放軍部隊作防務之用。<br />\n<br />\n本報早於2014年獨家報道，揭露。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨林卓廷駁斥保安局指：「國防外交係中央管，香港嘅防務就係解放軍，話防務用途但又唔係軍事，噏咩？防務唔係軍事咩？睇唔到有咩分別！」他揶揄「。。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PHmZRU_Qzqqh3x75uL_JSal_w7M=/2069x1319/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OF6A5CNIKVCGVMAYRDVYRC4XO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPHmZRU_Qzqqh3x75uL_JSal_w7M%3D%2F2069x1319%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOF6A5CNIKVCGVMAYRDVYRC4XO4.jpg&h=3e61229d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■雷達站內石壆印有「忠诚坚毅」四字。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前英兵指或作偵測監聽用途<br />\n<br />\n有前華籍英兵指港英殖民時代，駐港英軍在大帽山上設雷達站，截聽內地訊息。有軍事專家則認為，所謂防務用途，可能是偵測或監聽，但直言雷達站所謂通訊裝置作防務用途，外界無從得知「擺咗咩喺度」。他諷刺當局，「軍事同防務冇乜分別，好明顯有兵（駐守）喺度，但又唔避忌，佢話擺遊樂場都可以㗎啦！」又直斥雷達站大字標題寫有「听党话 跟党走」標語，「仲驚死你睇唔到！」擔心香港有更多其他土地，被當局私下用作類似用途。<br />\n<br />\n保安局今凌晨回覆指出，用作。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Q9yI1-RDytbmyxrUtjboXwrfcpI=/1276x370/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SYTB7XFDBZHO3D4FODARBLBCW4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQ9yI1-RDytbmyxrUtjboXwrfcpI%3D%2F1276x370%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSYTB7XFDBZHO3D4FODARBLBCW4.gif&h=3fbd1c8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c0f62d376cee340624c6d767dfa6c1ff930db08","tid":2361528,"uid":260694,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T17:39:33.000Z","msg":"好撚正常，一國一制，支那港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}